/*
 * Error Test: E3038 - void function call passed to println
 *
 * Regression for #1483: `println(nothing())` used to leak to clang
 * with a raw "incompatible type 'void'" error. Typechecker now
 * rejects void expressions at builtin print-family call sites.
 */

do nothing() {}

do main() {
    println(nothing())
}
